# Cloudflare API token → 1Password bootstrap (no guessing)

0. **Operator mint ask (before dashboard mint):** paste [TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md) **Mint request discipline** — **token name**, **exact scopes**, **program values** (account/zone IDs, TTL, `op://`, Worker secret names, `store-cloudflare-token` metadata) — in the **same** chat message as the mint request. For **Token P0**, include the **Operator mint request** table on that page.

1. **Verify, do not assume:** run **`./scripts/report-ssot-cloudflare-1password-inventory.sh`** in a shell where **`op whoami`** exits **0** **in that same process** ([ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/ONEPASSWORD_CLI_SESSION_GATE_SSOT.md) **§3** — Cursor **integrated terminal** `op signin` does **not** propagate to **Agent “Run command”** shells). If the script exits **2** (`op_signed_out`), **stop** — do not claim vault contents; run **`eval "$(op signin)"`** (or **`./scripts/op-ensure-session.sh`**) **in that shell**, or have the operator run the script from a terminal they already signed in.
2. **Ingest (stdin only):** **`pbpaste | OP_INTERACTIVE_OP_UNLOCK=1 ./scripts/op-upsert-ssot-deploy-workers-api-token.sh`** for portfolio **`CF-SSOT-DEPLOY-WORKERS-API`** (or set **`SSOT_DEPLOY_OP_ITEM_TITLE`**). Same **`expires=`** + **`GET /user/tokens/verify`** pattern as **`op-upsert-g6-zone-waf-token-item.sh`**. **Token P0 (Email Service send):** **`pbpaste | ./scripts/with-op-service-account-env.sh ./scripts/op-upsert-p0-email-service-send-api-token.sh`** (Rust **`p0-op-materialize store-email-sending-token`** — item title **`CF-P0-EMAIL-SERVICE-SEND-API`** must match Cloudflare **Token name**); optional sibling **`credential-manager`** **`store-cloudflare-token`** when installed — [TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md) **Token P0-EMAIL-SERVICE-SEND**.
3. **Expiry email pressure:** schedule **`./scripts/automated-token-lifecycle.sh --action check-expiration --token-name "CF-SSOT-DEPLOY-WORKERS-API"`** daily with **`EMAIL_ALERT_HMAC_SECRET`** + **`EMAIL_ALERT_WORKER_URL`** (**`ROTATION_WARNING_DAYS`**, default **7**) — [TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md) **Token G6** policy applies to **any** monitored item title passed to **`--token-name`**.
4. **Canonical packets:** [TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/TOKEN_CREATION_CHECKLIST_SSOT.md) **§0.0** + **§0.0a** + **§0.0b** (**`op-developer-cloudflare-vault-standardize.sh`**: **`audit`**, **`stamp-notes`**, **`verify-cloudflare-bearers`** — no dashboard mint); playbook [AGENT_AUTOMATION_CLOUDFLARE_PLAYBOOK_SSOT.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/AGENT_AUTOMATION_CLOUDFLARE_PLAYBOOK_SSOT.md) **§1.2**; [CURSOR_1PASSWORD_DEVELOPER_VAULT_2026-04-27.md](https://github.com/centexmsp/repository-restructuring/blob/main/docs/CURSOR_1PASSWORD_DEVELOPER_VAULT_2026-04-27.md) **three-surface matrix** + **`op whoami`** per shell.
